## Configuration

Uses your Linear workflow configuration:

- **Team**: {{linear.teamName}} ({{linear.teamKey}})
- **Status Grouping**: Uses status definitions to group intelligently:
  - Active: Statuses with "working", "in progress", "review"
  - Paused: Statuses with "hold", "paused"
  - Blocked: Statuses with "feedback", "blocked", "waiting"

```javascript
// Fetch user's issues
const myIssues = await searchIssues({
  filter: {
    assignee: { id: { eq: currentUser.id } },
    state: { type: { nin: ["completed", "canceled"] } },
    team: { id: { eq: config.linear.teamId } }
  },
  orderBy: { updatedAt: "desc" }
});

// Group by status meaning
const grouped = groupByStatusMeaning(myIssues, config.linear.statuses);
```

